                        li Meeting host assigned to oversee the running and documenting of the retrospective.
                        // During the event
                        li The whole team attends the retrospective.
                        li All attendees contribute to the retrospective.
                        li Product Owner and colleagues attentive and actively contribute to proceedings.
                        li A "no name, no blame" culture prevails throughout the retrospective.
                        li Attendees feel safe to speak openly during the retrospective.
                        li Almost no topic is off limits.
                        li Anonymous feedback is allowed but not the norm.
                        li Meeting runs smoothly with all participants having equal opportunity to contribute.
                        li Team assesses both the positive and negative aspects of the sprint.   
